Package sagma.core.data.generator

Class Summary
BundledRandomNumberGenerator This generator generates randomly distributed numbers across an interval using a step function.
ConstantNumberGenerator Generates the same given number every time it's called
LinearNumberGenerator A LinearNumberGenerator returns a new number that incrementially increases/decreases depending upon the given parameters.
NumberGenerator A NumberGenerator generates a new number on request, where the new number is created from a defined set of rules.
RandomNumberGenerator Generates a random number using the specified options.
